## C√¢u 4
T√≠nh di·ªán t√≠ch h√¨nh ph·∫≥ng gi·ªõi h·∫°n b·ªüi $y = x^2$ v√† $y = 2x$ t·ª´ $x = 0$ ƒë·∫øn $x = 2$

**A)** $\frac{4}{3}$

**B)** $\frac{8}{3}$

**C)** $4$

**D)** $\frac{16}{3}$

**Gi·∫£i:**
Di·ªán t√≠ch c·∫ßn t√≠nh: $S = \int_0^2 |x^2 - 2x| dx$

T·ª´ $x = 0$ ƒë·∫øn $x = 2$: $x^2 - 2x = x(x-2) \leq 0$

N√™n $S = \int_0^2 (2x - x^2) dx = [x^2 - \frac{x^3}{3}]_0^2 = 4 - \frac{8}{3} = \frac{4}{3}$

V·∫≠y ƒë√°p √°n ƒë√∫ng l√† **A**.

