**C)** $\frac{2x}{x^2}$

**D)** $\frac{x}{x^2 + 1}$

**Gi·∫£i:**
S·ª≠ d·ª•ng c√¥ng th·ª©c ƒë·∫°o h√†m c·ªßa h√†m h·ª£p: $(\ln u)' = \frac{u'}{u}$

